<!--pages/statement/statement.wxml-->
<view class="card">
    <view class="card-title">
        <image class="card-title-img" src="{{statement}}" />
        <view class="card-title-font">
            软件声明
        </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card-container">
        <view class="card-container-title">
            <image class="card-container-title-img" src="{{message}}" />
            <view class="card-container-title-font">
                声明
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="card-container-text">
            {{miniprogram_name}}小程序 | {{information.type}}
        </view>

        <view class="card-container-text">
            {{information.author}} 
        </view>

        <view class="card-container-text">
            指导老师：{{information.teacher}}
        </view>


    </view>

    <view class="card-container">
        <view class="card-container-title">
            <image class="card-container-title-img" src="{{zhixie}}" />
            <view class="card-container-title-font">
                致谢
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="card-container-all">
            <text class="card-container-text" decode="true">&emsp;&emsp;感谢各位小程序开发者，小程序界面布局、开源代码、提供的思路给我提供了很大的帮助。</text>

            <image class="card-container-img" src="{{zhixie_kaifazhe}}" mode="widthFix" />

            <text class="card-container-text" decode="true">&emsp;&emsp;感谢B站分享技术视频的up主们，根据你们的教程使得能够快速上手小程序开发，能在较短的时间内产出小程序的原型，极大的降低了学习的时间成本。</text>

            <image class="card-container-img" src="{{zhixie_up}}" mode="widthFix" />
        </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card-container">
        <view class="card-container-title">
            <image class="card-container-title-img" src="{{notes}}" />
            <view class="card-container-title-font">
                开源代码
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="card-container-text" >
          作者首页 : https://github.com/Blizzard-cyber
        </view>

        <view class="card-container-text" >
          作者邮箱 : 369476975@qq.com
        </view>
        <view class="card-container-text" >
          GitHub : https://github.com/Blizzard-cyber/Campus-Navigation-System
        </view>
        <view class="card-container-text" >
          使用代码请遵守相关开源协议!
        </view>

    </view>

    <view class="bottom-font">
        云游成电校园导航  |  版权归开发者所有
    </view>
</view>